    "Id": "chassisdef_thunderbolt_TDR-12R",
    "Name": "Thunderbolt",
    "Details": "This variant, built on Tikonov and used by the Republic of the Sphere, is intended to anchor and support vehicle formations. With a top speed of 54 km/h it won't break any speed records, but can keep up with most battle armor and combat vehicle formations. The standard armor is replaced by Reflective Armor and ammunition has been stored in a CASE II-protected bay. The right arm carries a plasma rifle, while the right torso carries a pair of Thunderbolt 5 launchers. The left torso is equipped with a Clan-spec LRM-15, and the traditional medium lasers of the left torso have been replaced by three Small Variable Speed Pulse Lasers. The left arm carries a pair of standard medium lasers. Twelve double heat sinks handle the heat load.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Multi Trac</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>",
